          <p class='first-para'>
            The noble Baroness has given warning.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0643P0-04051'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0643P0_20030123_GCR_94' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
